{"tid":716384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李純恩：大哥就是大哥","createTime":"2018-06-25T08:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T22:57:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"085435b2b217f245eeaf22fec79f3f14ed3c4359","tid":716384,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"中國球迷興沖沖到俄羅斯看世界盃，不料俄羅斯人印了幾萬張假門票，數千中國球迷不幸中招，買了假門票，進不了球場真大門，掃興掃到家了。<br />\n<br />\n中國和俄羅斯師出同門，蘇聯老大哥、中國小弟弟，冥冥中有些相同的DNA，你能做得出的事情，我也做得出。以為今天只有中國人造假貨了，沒想到，老大哥始終是老大哥，隔了那麼多年，手藝未曾生疏過，小弟弟一個不慎，就着了道兒。<br />\n<br />\n這種假門票事件要是發生在美國、日本，甚至南韓，那就不得了了，憤怒的中國人民不知又是燒甚麼東西來抗議洩憤了。但說也奇怪，中國人民全世界容不得一粒沙子，就是對欺侮了自己幾十年的俄國人特別寬容，至今，俄羅斯在中國的大使館、領事館都很安全，門口沒有高聲叫罵的「示威群眾」，俄國人開的餐廳，也沒人砸玻璃「罷喝羅宋湯」。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，蘇聯老大哥的身影在中國人民心目中，還是很高大，加上習主席剛剛頒了個最高榮譽獎給俄羅斯的普京，稱他為「最好的知心好友」，與之相比，區區幾萬張世界盃假門票便不值一提了，中國人民，終於表現了一次風度，畢竟是大哥嘛！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2101093/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2101093%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2593%25A5%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2593%25A5&d=2cyo8dFeyNMIOGkW81WWsghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f2e46afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2101093/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e2842a23dcc2444fad51b62dfbf3a0047dd150","tid":716384,"uid":161003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29cbba9341639a3e28274ae85cec349e014cb22","tid":716384,"uid":33668,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國人民，終於表現了一次風度，<span style=\"color: red;\">畢竟是大哥嘛！</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2101093/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2101093%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2593%25A5%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2593%25A5&d=2cyo8dFeyNMIOGkW81WWsghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f2e46afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2101093/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑大陸做契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ed7efa1c7bc204988762761fb193da9887f58b","tid":716384,"uid":179322,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"佢啲專欄成日奶共<br />\n無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29077dcfc3fbcaadd45bc162a75643a25acbc51","tid":716384,"uid":33875,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"上海佬骨子裡同香港人一樣覺得鬼佬搞到自己繁榮穩定，「同胞」就滲入自己地方搞到污煙漳氣，見佢近幾年都忍唔住密密抽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa5c85845c1b16a8e34686412274d8fcd57dc61","tid":716384,"uid":60333,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"43ed7efa1c7bc204988762761fb193da9887f58b","tid":716384,"uid":179322,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"佢啲專欄成日奶共<br />\n無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"中文攞幾"},{"pid":"88d53554de4b2bef9cc15290a9b57493ca1bae42","tid":716384,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"19用佢名寫架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbd34574a042734f8c6e6aadd15dbbdfa9d4f57","tid":716384,"uid":19501,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"88d53554de4b2bef9cc15290a9b57493ca1bae42","tid":716384,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"19用佢名寫架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"李純恩抽強國啲文係幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d00a6b16bbad1da35bcd3e6c322f4aece19461","tid":716384,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfce85e426010aefe3d5e6b9e4a2222f2d5ad638","tid":716384,"uid":22736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"43ed7efa1c7bc204988762761fb193da9887f58b","tid":716384,"uid":179322,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"佢啲專欄成日奶共<br />\n無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"你文盲來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e65daf39f43683b0c32a7def1dc34a74ee24ff7","tid":716384,"uid":106204,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:21:21.000Z","msg":"世界盃期間，中國號稱運了十萬隻小龍蝦到俄羅斯，國人想像一下洋人喝啤酒，吃中國特色小龍蝦的情景，樂不可支。<br />\n<br />\n但內地傳媒到了俄羅斯後，遍尋不獲小龍蝦，到處打聽，不要說「羅宋」餐館，即使當地中餐館，也都沒聽說有祖國小龍蝦來訪之事。記者於是向揚言出口小龍蝦的中國公司打聽，也不得要領，估計又是一樁造假事件。<br />\n<br />\n中國人狂喜小龍蝦，全國各地到處都聽人說小龍蝦，據說都吃得上癮了，幾天不吃不舒服。我本來對此沒有興趣，但年前在上海拍美食節目，為明星廚藝比賽做評判，有一次內容說小龍蝦，這才嘗了一下。一嘗之下，就知道為甚麼吃了會上癮，因為煮小龍蝦的配料味道奇重，有麻辣，還有一種「十三香」，那種濃味吃過之後，舌頭適應了這麼重的味道，以後吃甚麼都覺得不夠味。<br />\n<br />\n這其實是把一條舌頭吃壞了，除了這種味道，其他都吃不出鮮美。所以，我試過一次之後，世上美味何其之多，讓自己的味覺栽在這小龍蝦身上，太不值得。<br />\n<br />\n撰文 : 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n欄名 : 天地良心"},{"pid":"9e0d3972389e6d544befe4420c170e864b8f7dd4","tid":716384,"uid":28652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"睇節目覺得佢冇乜特別 估唔到啲文又幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e54090d5dbab7fb092f6b8273deeb94204e8ea","tid":716384,"uid":52972,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"88d53554de4b2bef9cc15290a9b57493ca1bae42","tid":716384,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"19用佢名寫架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"就咁睇我都以為係才子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5587b04d0230a09be9b728d43e360d20db8451e","tid":716384,"uid":166434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"43ed7efa1c7bc204988762761fb193da9887f58b","tid":716384,"uid":179322,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"佢啲專欄成日奶共<br />\n無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"你中文閱讀拎咩<br />\n<br />\n利申五星星"},{"pid":"f8e75d8aa76de7f1445268c8a4a776cd213f3f5b","tid":716384,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"罷喝羅宋湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s